{
  "stem": "22660.1",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "And Max Warburg, this famous banker-- he was really in Germany what the Rothschilds were in France-- did a fact-finding tour all through Europe, and came back and had a dinner for the family.",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "And said, you know what, as bad as it is here, it's much worse in the other countries.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "And almost-- not almost-- did say, don't leave.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "And my grandfather Cohen, my father's father, said there you are.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "And you want to know it better than Max Warburg.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "They simply did not believe it would hit them.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes we did, as we grew older.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "When we were nine and ten, matter of fact, two of the friends that I was lucky enough to meet later on in life again, I remember I was playing with one of them, Lilo Baer was her name.",
      "word_count": 39
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Her family had shoe stores all over Germany.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And we were playing, and the mail came.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And they already had hoped that they could immigrate to the United States.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And she was so anxious that we took the letter and over steam-- we had a kettle, and we steamed the letter open.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And she could see that they would get the affidavit from some relatives that they had in the United States.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So yes, we did discuss it.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We did discuss it.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We got scared now.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "As two or three years passed, we became frightened.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And we wondered what would happen to us, we really did.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "What things took place that frightened you?",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, for one thing, beginning of 1938, the Gestapo started to come to pick up the men.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And so they came to my house numerous times.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And my father already would be visiting friends and customers and relatives all over Germany so that they wouldn't find him at home.",
      "word_count": 23
    }
  ],
